abstract.text: Indicator that shows a horizontal collection of dots.
Adds a custom view as a pagers indicator view
A container view that shows multiple pages by horizontal scrolling between them.
This library provides a pager container view that organizes its child views in horizontal
scrollable fashion. It also comes with a rich indicator that complements a pager with quick access
to any page and features such as scrubbing and quick scrolling through the pagers content.
to a pager in the View hierachy
